{"tid":1671181,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王婆婆 8.11 後未露面　朱凱廸：警方答應代為聯絡家人","createTime":"2019-10-23T10:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T21:29:30.000Z","uid":68738,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"84ee1a195a72dcfb456a4856796d032b110055b9","tid":1671181,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/eongborbor-06_2BEnA_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Feongborbor-06_2BEnA_1200x0.png&h=82773949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過去經常在抗爭現場揮舞港英旗的「王婆婆」王鳳瑤，對上一次出現在抗爭活動現場，已經是 8.11 在太古站，外界一直關注她的去向；一直跟進她情況的民主派議員朱凱廸在 fb 發文，指過去一個半月，關心王婆婆的市民以不同方法尋找她的家人，並在網上募集了 2 萬元，今日已將籌款消息通知警方，警方答應會轉達王婆婆的家人，請家人和朱凱廸聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸又表示，自王婆婆 8.11 失蹤後，9 月初保安局曾透露她身在中國大陸，但只會向家人交代她的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%8E%8B%E5%A9%86%E5%A9%86-8-11-%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%AA%E9%9C%B2%E9%9D%A2-%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%E5%BB%B8-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%AD%94%E6%87%89%E4%BB%A3%E7%82%BA%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%25A9%2586%25E5%25A9%2586-8-11-%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%259C%25AA%25E9%259C%25B2%25E9%259D%25A2-%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%2587%25B1%25E5%25BB%25B8-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25AD%2594%25E6%2587%2589%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=55eafa37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%25A9%2586%25E5%25A9%2586-8-11-%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%259C%25AA%25E9%259C%25B2%25E9%259D%25A2-%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%2587%25B1%25E5%25BB%25B8-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25AD%2594%25E6%2587%2589%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&h=a0